snippet.title: Honest Trailers | Freddy vs Jason
snippet.description:
It’s time for the ultimate cash-grab / showdown: Freddy vs. Jason! These two horror icons clash in the silliest, least scary movie since Scary Movie. Ah well, at least Hollywood learned their lesson and never resorted to cheap team-up films again, right? Right???

Shout-out to Zack Ward for making another cameo!
IG - @Totalzackward
Cameo - https://cameo.com/DarthFarkus

Only In Theaters December 5.

A spoof that crosses Downton Abbey with Airplane! and Monty Python, Fackham Hall follows loveable pick-pocket Eric Noone (Radcliffe) as he lands a job at a unique English manor house. He quickly rises through the ranks, and a forbidden romance with lady-of-the-house Rose Davenport (McKenzie) blossoms. But when an unexpected murder occurs, Eric gets framed - leaving Rose and her family’s future perilously uncertain.

snippet.title: You can get a FREE Hypercharge Skin! #ScaryDoors

♦️ There are 20 rewards hidden behind doors, including the Manga Kenji Hypercharge Skin for FREE!
♦️ Only 10 doors can be opened in total, one per day, except for the last day, when you can open 3 doors at the same time!

🔸 Complete 80 Million Quests every day and earn a key that opens a door
🔸 To pick a door, the community must vote for it in the in-game News and the door with the highest votes will be opened the next day!

Winners will be picked after the event ends on November 5th!
